<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> A.D. Sakharov: <a href="http://www.jetpletters.ac.ru/ps/1643/article_25090.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.jetpletters.ac.ru/ps/1643/article_25090.pdf" rel="nofollow">Quark-Muonic Currents and Violation of CP Invariance</a>, Pisma Zh. Eksp. Teor. Fiz. 5: 36-39 (1967); translation in JETP Lett. 5: 27-30 (1967)</li>
